  npcName: "Prdom\xEDr \u0160oustalump"
  dialogueLines:
  - We thought guarding it was enough.
  - "Turns out\u2026\nnothing like this survives by being guarded forever."
  - Something always has to step closer.
  recipesToUnlock:
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: f0c535d535ee3ad40b718f2509ca7e6e, type: 2}
  ambientDialogue:
  - Your shadow is getting longer. Just an observation.
  - The ones before you... they had such hope. It was delicious.
  - Guard it if you want. Entropy always wins.
  - I float because the ground rejects me. Or maybe I reject it.
